The Facebook LIVE will be held at 2pm today so set your clocks! Richard will be joined by our host Pandora Forsyth to discuss the latest developments in the Royal Family as Prince Charles' letters to Jimmy Saville are released and Meghan Markle tries to trademark a word from the 1540s. There are no doubts it has been a big week in royal news, with letters reportedly written by Prince Charles to Jimmy Savile being featured in a Netflix documentary. The show looks into how Savile made contacts at the highest levels of society, reaching royals, politicians and leading British personalities. The latest move will be discussed Live the Royal Roundup Facebook series as the Sussexes could be at odds with companies that use the word in their names. The duchess has also cut ties with a UK pet charity in an interesting mood.